    "Title": "Find XenoThreat Captive and Stolen Data",
    "TitleKey": "cfp_missingperson_sabotage_servers_H_XT_title_001",
    "Description": "The family of ~mission(TargetName), a Citizens for Prosperity courier, has been in contact with me with the terrible news that they never arrived back home. We learned that ~mission(TargetName|First) was captured by XenoThreat while transporting some critical data. \n\nWe need you to search ~mission(Location|Address) and see if you can learn what has become of ~mission(TargetName|First) and then destroy any XenoThreat servers that may contain stolen data.\n\nThank you,\n \nLima Endicott\nLead Dispatcher\nCitizens for Prosperity",
    "DescriptionKey": "cfp_missingperson_sabotage_servers_H_XT_desc_001",
    "DisplayDescription": "The family of [TargetName], a Citizens for Prosperity courier, has been in contact with me with the terrible news that they never arrived back home. We learned that [TargetName|First] was captured by XenoThreat while transporting some critical data. \n\nWe need you to search Remote Outpost near [NearbyLocation] and see if you can learn what has become of [TargetName|First] and then destroy any XenoThreat servers that may contain stolen data.\n\nThank you,\n \nLima Endicott\nLead Dispatcher\nCitizens for Prosperity",
